  "cost_gp": 4000.0,
  "description": "Wondrous Item, Rare (Requires Attunement)\n\nThis robe is adorned with eyelike patterns. While you wear the robe, you gain the following benefits:\n\nAll-Around Vision. The robe gives you Advantage on Wisdom (Perception) checks that rely on sight.\n\nSpecial Senses. You have Darkvision and Truesight, both with a range of 120 feet.\n\nDrawbacks. A Light spell cast on the robe or a Daylight spell cast within 5 feet of the robe gives you the &amp;Reference[Blinded] condition for 1 minute. At the end of each of your turns, you make a Constitution saving throw (DC 11 for Light or DC 15 for Daylight), ending the condition on yourself on a success.",
